DESCRIPTION:Come build community through 45 minutes of chair yoga. Seated in a chair\, we will move gently\, mindfully\, stretching\, and finding our alignment both internally and externally. Breath is emphasized as is a smile. Modifications are always provided\, and we move at a pace that is appropriate for all levels and all ages.
